Generated artifacts from svalbard import.

This directory is populated automatically:

  - ZIM files from --bundle, web crawls, and media imports
  - .source.yaml metadata sidecars for each artifact
  - .staging/ temporary build directories

Files here are gitignored. To rebuild a bundle:

  svalbard import --bundle my-library sources/topic/*.pdf

To attach a generated artifact to a drive:

  svalbard attach local:my-library /path/to/drive
